loads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/gun-interactive">Gun Interactive</a>向多人恐怖游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-texas-chainsaw-massacre"><em>《德州电锯杀人狂》</em></a>的粉丝保证，该游戏不会遭受与<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/friday-the-13th-the-game">《十三号星期五：游戏》</a>相同的命运。</em></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/horror-video-game-too-scary-2831566">恐怖视频游戏会太可怕吗？</a></strong></li></ul><p> <em>《德州电锯杀人狂》</em>将于 8 月 18 日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/ps4">PS4</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/ps5">PS5</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>上推出，目前游戏的评价已经基本正面。尽管人们期待肯塔基州开发商推出另一款授权的非对称游戏，但人们对这个特定项目的寿命提出了疑问。</p><p> “ <em>《Friday The 13th》</em>周围的情况本质上比<em>德克萨斯州</em>更加复杂，”创意总监罗尼·霍布斯 (Ronnie Hobbs) 在接受<a href="https://www.pcgamesn.com/the-texas-chainsaw-massacre/friday-the-thirteenth" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>PCGamesN</em></a>采访时解释道。</p><p> “对于<em>德克萨斯州</em>，我们直接与知识产权的唯一所有者 Kim Henkel 打交道。在整个过程中我们一直与他密切合作，不仅从创意角度，而且从法律角度。在整个过程中，我们一直尽可能勤奋，以确保事情顺利进行。”他证实。 </p><figure id="attachment_3483641" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3483641" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3483641" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/texas-chainsaw-massacre-is-not-shutting-down-any-time-soon-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3483641" class="wp-caption-text"> “德州电锯大屠杀”图片来源：Sumo Digital</figcaption></figure><p> 2018 年， <em>《Friday The 13th》</em>联合创作者维克多·米勒 (Victor Miller) 对电影导演兼制片人肖恩·坎宁安 (Sean Cunningham) 提起诉讼，这意味着 Gun Interactive 在法律诉讼期间被禁止向游戏添加任何新内容。</p><p>最终，由于 Gun Interactive 和 Miller 之间的许可讨论结果， <em>Friday The 13th</em>将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/friday-the-13th-the-game-to-receive-final-patch-and-stop-future-support-2808235">2023 年 12 月 31 日退市。</a></p><p>不过，这些事件并没有让开发商陷入困境。 “《 <em>Friday The 13th》</em>取得成功后，有很多潜在的追求者联系我们，希望将他们的 IP 变成游戏，”Hobbs 透露。</p><p> “我们花了很长时间整理和权衡我们的选择，最后被介绍给 Kim Henkel。一旦我们发现双方都对创造一款游戏抱有极大的兴趣，我们很快就知道<em>德克萨斯州</em>将成为我们的下一个项目，”创意总监说道。</p><p>在其他地方，最近分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hollowbody"><em>《Hollowbody》</em></a>的早期游戏片段，这是一款受《<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/silent-hill"><em>寂静岭</em></a>》启发的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/british-horror-game-hollowbody-reveals-five-minutes-of-silent-hill-inspired-gameplay-3424000">“黑色科技”生存恐怖游戏，背景设定在英国的一个世界末日城市</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-texas-chain-saw-massacre-dev-talks-about-the-friday-the-13th-elephant-in-the-room-3483623">《德克萨斯电锯杀人狂》的开发者表示，它不会遭受与</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现的《13 号星期五》相同的命运。</p> ;
