 https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_portishead_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_portishead_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_portishead_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_portishead_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/portishead">Portishead</a>的 Beth Gibbons 与阿富汗女子乐队 Miraculous Love Kids 合作翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joy-division">Joy Division</a>的《Atmosphere》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a>的《Heroes》。</p><p>这张专辑的标题是《Atmosphere/Heroes》，将这两首歌融合在一起，吉本斯与乐队一起主唱这首歌曲。您可以查看下面的视频。</p><p>吉本斯在一份新闻稿中（通过<a href="https://pitchfork.com/news/portisheads-beth-gibbons-sings-joy-division-and-bowie-with-the-miraculous-love-kids-watch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Pitchfork</em></a> ）表示：“我非常荣幸能在 Miraculous Love Kids 翻唱歌曲《Atmosphere/Heroes》中担任嘉宾，并成为这些勇敢美丽的阿富汗女孩的代言人。”</p><p>此次释放标志着塔利班重新控制阿富汗、妇女权利和自由受到限制已有两年。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="神奇的爱情儿童-氛围/英雄以贝丝·吉本斯为特色（波蒂斯黑德）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KBtck4Rk3tk?start=140&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> The women in Miraculous Love Kids fled Kabul in Afghanistan, for Pakistan with their families and formed the band alongside American musician and activist Lanny Cordola.</p><p> Cordola said he first met Gibbons in Islamabad, “just days after the Taliban takeover.”</p><p> He added: “She confirmed her support and extended a generosity of spirit to the girls that was invaluable as she is truly one of the great voices in the world today. The words exemplify the plight of the harshly oppressed people of the world. In particular, the girls and women of Afghanistan, where the Miraculous Love Kids hail from.”</p><p> The Miraculous Love Kids have previously teamed up with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/serj-tankian">Serj Tankian</a> in the past.</p><p> Meanwhile, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a> recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-noel-gallagher-cover-joy-divisions-love-will-tear-us-apart-3450638">covered Joy Division&#39;s &#39;Love Will Tear Us Apart&#39; with the BBC Concert Orchestra earlier this year</a> .</p><p> The former <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> chief appeared on the BBC Radio 2 Piano Room series to perform the classic.</p><p> Elsewhere, earlier this year <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">St. Vincent</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-roots">The Roots</a> covered <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-st-vincent-and-the-roots-haunting-cover-portisheads-glory-box-3411347">Portishead&#39;s &#39;Glory Box&#39; on</a> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-st-vincent-and-the-roots-haunting-cover-portisheads-glory-box-3411347">The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon</a> .</em></p><p> Remaining faithful to the original 1995 single, the atmospheric collaboration saw Annie Clark put her own spin on the song&#39;s electrifying guitar solo, and deliver a powerful and haunting vocal.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-portisheads-beth-gibbons-cover-joy-division-and-david-bowie-with-afghan-girl-band-3483607">Watch Portishead&#39;s Beth Gibbons cover Joy Division and David Bowie with Afghan girl band</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
